createNewCertificate(string,string,strin.details: function is called every time someone wants to register a new marriage certificate

params.city: = city where the marriage is registered
params.country: = country where the marriage is registered
params.firstName: = first name of the spouse initiating the certificate
params.id: = id provided by spouse initiating the certificate
params.lastName: = last name of the spouse initiating the certificate
params.otherSpouseAddress: = address of other spouse from which the confirmation has to come
params.otherSpouseFirstName: = first name of the other spouse
params.otherSpouseLastName: = last name of the other spouse

confirmMarriage(bytes32).notice: 2nd spouse confirms the marriage certificate and makes it valid
